<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>HOTLINE</title>
</head>
<body>
  <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
		style="margin: 10px auto;
			min-width: 320px;
			max-width: 540px;
			width: 100%;
			font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background-color: #efefef;
      color: #707070;
      border: 2px solid #efefef;
      border-top: 15px solid #11888c;">
		<tbody>
			<tr>
				<td style="padding-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;">
					<p style="text-align: center; font-size: 29px;"><span style="color: #11888c; font-weight: bold;">HOTLINE</span>REPORT</p>
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="text-align: center;">
					<p style="font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 0;">Thanks for using Hotline Report</p>
					<p style="font-size: 22px; margin: 0;">Your report number is:</p>
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase;">
					<p style="font-size: 34px;
          margin: 10px auto;
          background-color: #ffffff;
          padding: 20px;
          width: 70%;
          color: #11888c;
          font-weight: bold;"><%= reference %></p>
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase;">
					<a href="<%=URL_FRONT%>/follow-up" target="_blank" style="font-size: 20px;
          margin: 10px auto;
          background-color: #ffd5ee;
          padding: 10px 20px;
          width: 70%;
          height: 25px;
          color: #363636;
          font-weight: bold;
          display: block;
          text-decoration: none;">FOLLOW UP</p>
				</a>
			</tr>
      <tr>
				<td style="text-align: center;">
					<p style="font-size: 20px;
          width: 75%;
          margin: 10px auto;">You will need this <span style="color: #585858; font-weight: bold;">REPORT NUMBER</span> and a <span style="color: #585858; font-weight: bold;">PASSWORD</span> you created to access the system for follow ups</p>
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="padding: 30px 50px;">
					<p style="font-size: 10px;">“The purpose of this page is to ensure that all individuals working on this production have a channel to report safety, workplace or ethical concerns. It is our hope that individuals feel comfortable reporting any issues to production supervision; however, if for any reason you are not, we encourage you to use this hotline. <br><br>The hotline is provided by GRUPO CINCOVEINTICINCO SAS and is available to production companies, their respective employees, crew members, talent, associated vendors, and other partners directly tied to a production. The reports are confidential and anonymous, unless you voluntarily provide personal information to support addressing and investigating your case. <br><br>Please be advised that it is expected an average of 24 hours to receive a response on reports submitted via this hotline. If this is an EMERGENCY, please immediately notify your department head, production leadership, production HR, safety consultant, or local authorities. Timely reporting is critical in addressing issues as well as preventing injuries or accidents. Remember that retaliation against any reporting party who raises a concern in good faith will not be tolerated.”</p>
				</td>
			</tr>
      <tr>
				<td style="text-align: center;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 11px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding-bottom: 10px;">
					<p style="color: #11888c; font-weight: bold;">LEGAL TERMS | DATA POLICY</p>
					<p style="width: 50%; margin: auto;">COPYRIGHT © 2022 GRUPO CINCOVEINTICINCO SAS. ALL RIGTHS RESERVED</p>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</tbody>
	</table>
</body>
</html>


